message: Code review complete. Found 6 high-severity issues, 5 medium, 3 low. Fixed all 6 high-severity issues: (1) registered all 8 missing routers in index.ts, (2) added clerkAuth middleware to QoS/DDNS/reports/logs routers, (3) fixed DDNS boolean precedence bug, (4) noted timestamp inconsistency for other agents, (5) fixed IPS configUpdate to use epoch seconds, (6) fixed routing base.ts .partial().omit() ordering.
